GitBreakDown is an extension that can analyze the health of your repository by analyzing various metrics and sorting by rank.
Some of these metrics are:
* Issues
* branchs
* Commits
* Pull requests

They are analyzed by time, between open closed, number of comments by users, PR accepted or not and many other features.

In our ranking it is possible to determine weights for each metric according to the user's need.


For more information contact: gitbreakdown@gmail.com

To contribute and access our unstable versions go to: https://github.com/fga-eps-mds/2019.2-Git-Breakdown
